{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "叶翔与孟星魂在草地饮酒密谈，叶翔警告孟星魂他所见到的灰衣杀人者是顶尖刺客，曾为孙玉伯效力，劝孟星魂远离孙玉伯。孟星魂透露在孙玉伯花园见到此人杀害黄山三友，叶翔揭示此人嗜血养鱼的怪癖。高老大向孟星魂通报万鹏王的动向，安排孟星魂跟踪屠大鹏，等待万鹏王与孙玉伯开战的时机刺杀孙玉伯。王二呆和夜猫子奉命潜入武老刀家，王二呆用绞索杀害武老刀，夜猫子用药迷倒小武并掳走黛黛。老伯得知律香川带回的消息后，判断万鹏王即将发动攻势，紧急召回孙剑并调动鹰组。一个自称姓何的刺客被捕后只反复说我姓何，老伯识破其背后有严密组织，决定放他回去以追踪幕后主使。孟星魂发现小何被老伯故意放走以追查幕后人，决定暗中保护小何并清除跟踪者。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你什么时候回来的？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "刚才。",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "一回来就来找我？到底是我们交情不同。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "坐下来，先喝杯酒再告诉我是为了什么事找我。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "好，现在告诉我，究竟什么事？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你常说，世上有两种人，一种是杀人的，一种是被杀的。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "每个人将人分类的法子都不同，我这种分类的法子并不正确。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你将世人如此分类，因为你是杀人的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "大多数杀人的，常常也就是被杀的。",
      "tone": "苦涩",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "有没有例外？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你是不是问，有没有人能永远杀人，而不被杀。",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这种人很少，简直太少了。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你知道有几个？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我就是其中一个，因为现在别人已不屑杀我。",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "除了你还有谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你是不是看到了一个很可怕的杀人者？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "他是个很普通的人，不高也不矮，不胖也不瘦。",
      "tone": "描述",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你没有看到他的脸？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "否定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他杀人的时候，是不是穿着一身暗灰色的衣服？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你知道他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他杀人后，是不是立刻将死者的血，抹在自己脸上？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "不错，就是这个人。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不知道，没有人知道他是谁，只不过下次你再见到他时，最好走得远些，越远越好。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "干这一行的行头并非只有我们两个，也许比你想像中还要多。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这本就是一行很古怪的职业，聂政、荆轲、专诸，就都是我们的同行。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这几个人虽然很有名，但却不能算做这一行的好手。",
      "tone": "评价",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你说过，干我们这一行的就不能有名，有名就不是好手。",
      "tone": "认同",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不错，要干这一行就得牺牲很多事：声名、家庭、地位、子女、朋友，一样都不能有。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "所以，我想绝没有人是自己愿意干这一行的，除非是疯子。",
      "tone": "苦涩",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "就算不是疯子，慢慢也会变疯的。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "但这一行中也有人是天生的疯子，只有这种人才是真正的好手，因为只有他们杀人时才能完全不动心，所以他们永远不会觉得厌倦，手也永远不会软。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你刚才说的那个人就是其中一个，也是最疯的一个。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "所以，他也是其中最好的一个？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "一点也不错，据我所知，这世上绝没有第二个人能比得上他。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你也比不上他，也许你比他冷静，比他聪明，甚至比他快，但你也不行，因为你不疯！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "你看过他杀人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "除了亲眼见到之外，没有人能形容他杀人的那种方法，他杀人时好像没有将对方看成一个人。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "那时他自己也不是一个人了。",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "据说这人退休很久，你是在哪里见到他的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "孙玉伯的花园里。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他杀的是谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "黄山三友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "为什么原因？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "因为他们得罪了孙玉伯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我早就想到他背后必定还有个人主使，却想不到是孙玉伯。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "赶快将孙玉伯这个人忘记，最好忘得干干净净。",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我忘不了。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "忘不了也要忘，否则你就得死，而且死得很快，因为你就算能杀了孙玉伯，这人也一定会杀了你！",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "别人当然不会知道是谁杀孙玉伯的，更找不到你，但是他能。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "他也知道世上有你这么样一个人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他知道，他第一眼看到我时，就已知道我这人是干什么的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他既然能看出我，当然也一定能看得出你。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我没有让他看到，只不过",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不过怎样？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他既然知道你这么样一个人，孙玉伯死了后，他想必就能追到这里来。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我忘不了。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你不信他能杀得死你？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "就算他杀不死你，但你若知道有这么样一个人随时随地都在暗中窥伺着你，等着你，你还能活得下去？",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "所以我只有先杀了他！",
      "tone": "决绝",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "杀他？你想杀他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "他也是个人。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你连他是个怎么样的人都不知道，怎能杀得了他？",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "我虽然不知道，但你却一定知道。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "回避",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "挽留",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他杀人，因为他不喜欢人，但是他喜欢血。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_ye_xiang",
      "text": "血？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "叶翔",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他不是喜欢吃鱼，是喜欢养鱼，养鱼的人并不多。",
      "tone": "神秘",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你没有在那里等我。",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我也没有走。",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你跟叶翔好像有很多话好说。",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "叶翔有没有在你面前说起过我？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "没有，从来没有。",
      "tone": "否定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我已知道孙玉伯为什么要派律香川去找万鹏王了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "孙玉伯有个老朋友，叫武老刀，武老刀的儿子爱上了万鹏王的家姬，万鹏王不答应，所以孙玉伯叫律香川去要人。",
      "tone": "叙述",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "结果呢？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "万鹏王已经将那小姑娘送给武老刀。而且还送了笔很厚的嫁妆。",
      "tone": "叙述",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "那么这件事岂非已结束？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "没有结束，刚开始。你想，万鹏王会是这么听话的人？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "照我看，万鹏王这么做，只是要孙玉伯不再对他有警戒之心，然后他才好向孙玉伯下手！",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "只要他下手，就必定是重重的一击！",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "所以他要将屠大鹏调回去。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "据我所知，除了屠大鹏外，金鹏、怒鹏，这两坛的坛主也已经离开了自己分坛的所在地，走的正是往十二飞鹏堡去的那条路。",
      "tone": "叙述",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你认为他们立刻就要对孙玉伯有所行动？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不错，只要他们一出手，你的机会就来了！",
      "tone": "兴奋",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你是不是要我在暗中跟踪屠大鹏？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不错，你了解他们的行动后才能把握机会，但是你绝不能让别人先下手，你一定要自己亲手杀死孙玉伯。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "服从",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "屠城是几个人来的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "只有三个人，由此可见他们这次的行踪很秘密。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "另外还有两个人是谁？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "一个是屠城的贴身随从，叫王二呆，但我却知道他非但一点也不呆，而且还是个极厉害的角色，呆相只不过是装给别人看的。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "还有个叫夜猫子，这人是个下五门的小贼，武功虽不值得重视，却是个用熏香蒙汗药的好手，屠城这次带着他回来显然有特别的用处。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他们什么时候走？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "屠城这次行色虽匆忙，但还是舍不得立刻走，现在金钏儿正在陪他，我想，金钏儿能留他一晚上。",
      "tone": "轻松",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我在想，能被金钏儿留住一晚的人，必定做不了十二飞鹏帮的第一号打手。",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "近来你好像已学会了很多，而且学得很快。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我非学不可。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "speaker_name": "武老刀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "儿子都已娶妻成亲，我还能不老么？",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "speaker_name": "武老刀",
      "listener": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "text": "你是不是想找老宋他们，他们都在外面厨房里喝酒。",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王二呆",
      "listener": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "text": "我就是找你。",
      "tone": "醉态",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "speaker_name": "武老刀",
      "listener": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "text": "找我？有何贵干？",
      "tone": "奇怪",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "speaker_name": "武老刀",
      "listener": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "text": "你有话跟我说？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "speaker_name": "武老刀",
      "listener": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "text": "你说吧！",
      "tone": "催促",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王二呆",
      "listener": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "text": "我要",
      "tone": "喘息",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "speaker_name": "武老刀",
      "listener": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "text": "你要干什么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王二呆",
      "listener": "char_wu_lao_dao",
      "text": "我要杀了你！",
      "tone": "凶狠",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_er_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王二呆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说要杀你就杀你，我从来不骗人的。",
      "tone": "傻笑",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "小武",
      "listener": "char_dai_dai",
      "text": "你永远是我的了，是不是？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "黛黛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wu",
      "text": "我一直都是你的！",
      "tone": "甜蜜",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "这人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "他犯了什么错误？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他想杀我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你不妨再问问，看看是不是能问得出什么？",
      "tone": "指示",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_xiao_he",
      "text": "你贵姓？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_he",
      "speaker_name": "小何",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "我姓何。",
      "tone": "麻木",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_xiao_he",
      "text": "大名？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_he",
      "speaker_name": "小何",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "我姓何。",
      "tone": "麻木",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_xiao_he",
      "text": "是谁叫你来的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_he",
      "speaker_name": "小何",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "我姓何。",
      "tone": "麻木",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "这人必定受过极严格的训练，能如此训练下属的人并不多。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "你认为那人是",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "是不是送他回去？",
      "tone": "请示",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "放他回去。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "不必去。",
      "tone": "断然",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他现在必定已经死了！",
      "tone": "哀痛",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "告诉鸽组的人，所有的人全都放弃轮休，一齐出动去找孙剑，无论他在干什么，都叫他立刻快马赶回来，片刻不得耽误。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "去将鹰组的人立刻带来。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "speaker_name": "律香川",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "text": "我应该再去看武老刀，现在他说不定已有危险。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "没有也许，像万鹏王那种人，绝不会令人感觉到危险，等那人感觉到危险的时候，必定已经活不成了。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你懂了么？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "你懂了就好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "他不说，并不是怕别的，而是我们一对他用刑，他立刻会无缘无故晕过去。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "我只问你，有谁从这里逃出去过没有？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "假如真有人从这里逃出去，会是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_bo",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉伯",
      "listener": "char_lv_xiang_chuan",
      "text": "像那样厉害的角色，你有本事一拳将他击倒？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 7
    }
  ],
